<main>
    <div id="editform">
        <h2>Edit Agency</h2>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
                <span class="timestamp-display">Last Updated</span>
                <span class="timestamp-display" id="timestamp-data"><%= organization.last_update %></span>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <button id="script-button">Show Call Script</button>
    <form action="/admin/editconfirmation" id="adminedit" method="POST" >
        
        <input name="_method" class="hidden" value="PUT">
        <input name="id" class="hidden" value=<%= organization.organization_id %> >
        <p class="script hidden">Hello, my name is __________ and I am a volunteer for Real Change.  Your services are listed in the Emerald City Resource Guide.  We are gearing up to print the third edition and need to verify your services. <br>Do you have a moment to confirm what we have in the guide is still correct or update your listing? <br><span class="emphasis">If yes, proceed.  If no, ask for a good call back time or contact phone number.</span></p>
        <p class="script hidden">What is your name and role at the agency so we can follow up with any questions? <br> <span class="emphasis">Enter contact information below.</span></p>
        <h3>Main Contact</h3>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
            <span>Name</span>
            <textarea name="contact_name" type="text"><%= organization.contact_name %></textarea>
          </label>
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
            <span>Title</span>
            <textarea name="contact_title" type="text"><%= organization.contact_title %></textarea>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
            <span>Phone</span>
            <textarea name="contact_phone" type="text"><%= organization.contact_phone %></textarea>
            </label>
        <fieldset>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
            <span>Email</span>
            <textarea name="contact_email" type="text"><%= organization.contact_email %></textarea>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <h3>Agency</h3>
        <p class="script hidden"><span class="emphasis">Read the agency name below aloud.</span> Is this the correct title of your agency?</p>
        <fieldset>
            <label >
                <span>Name</span>
                <textarea name="name" type="text" required><%= organization.organization_name %></textarea>
            </label> 
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
                <span>Website</span>
                <textarea name="website" type="text"><%= organization.website %></textarea>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <p class="script hidden">The phone number listed in the guidebook will be called by individuals seeking services.  Is this the correct phone number? <br><span class="emphasis">Read phone number below aloud.</span></p>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
                <span>Phone</span>
                <textarea name="phone_number" type="text" class="big"><%= organization.phone_number %></textarea>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <p class="script hidden">Is this address correct for people walking in during business hours to find services? <br><span class="emphasis">Read address below aloud.</span></p>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
                <span>Address</span>
                <textarea name="org_address" type="text" class="big"><%= organization.org_address %></textarea>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset>
                <label>
                    <span>Zip Code</span>
                    <input name="zipcode" type="text" pattern="[0-9]{5}" value=<%= organization.zipcode %> class="zip"></textarea>
                </label>
        </fieldset>
        <p class="script hidden">What hours are you open for people to walk in?</p>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
                <span>Hours</span>
                <textarea name="schedule" type="text" class="big"><%= organization.schedule %></textarea>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <p class="script hidden">Your agency description should be a brief, simple summary of the services someone can access when they come to your agency.  Do not list services that are not available for homeless and low-income individuals.  I will read your agency description, and then you can let me know if anything needs to be updated or changed. <br><span class="emphasis">Read description and category options below.</span><br></p>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
                <span>Description</span>
                <textarea name="org_description" type="text" class="bigger"><%= organization.org_description %></textarea>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset>
            <label>
                <span>Genders Served</span>
                <div id="genderopts">
                <label><input name="gender" type="radio" value="men only"
                <% if (organization.gender === 'men only') { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >Men Only</label>
                <label><input name="gender" type="radio" value="women only"
                <% if (organization.gender === 'women only') { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >Women Only</label>
                <label><input name="gender" type="radio" value="no restrictions"
                <% if (organization.gender === 'no restrictions') { %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >No Restrictions </label>
                </div>
            </label>
        </fieldset>
        </div>
        <div id="allcats">
        <div id="population">
            <h3>Target Populations </h3>
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[4]" value="24"
                <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(24) >= 0){ %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >Senior Citizens</label> 
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[5]" value="18"
                <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(18) >= 0){ %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >Immigrants or Refugees</label> 
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[6]" value="27"
                <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(27) >= 0){ %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >Survivors of Violence</label> 
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[0]" value="14" 
                <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(14) >= 0){ %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >People of Color</label> 
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[1]" value="13"
                <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(13) >= 0){ %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >Native & Indigenous People</label> 
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[2]" value="20"
                <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(20) >= 0){ %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >LGBTQIA+</label> 
            <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[3]" value="29"
                <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(29) >= 0){ %>
                    checked
                <% } %>
                >Veterans</label> 
            </div>
        <div id="services">
            <h3>Services Offered</h3>
            <section id="basic-needs">
                <h4>Basic Needs</h4>
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[7]" value="1"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(1) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Emergency and Crisis Lines</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[8]" value="3"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(3) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Hygiene Services</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[9]" value="4"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(4) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Encampments</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[10]" value="6"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(6) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Day Centers</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[11]" value="12"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(12) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Food Assistance</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[12]" value="17"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(17) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Housing Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[13]" value="25"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(25) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Shelters</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[14]" value="5"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(5) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Clothing Services</label> 
            </section>
            <section id="health">
                <h4>Health</h4>
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[15]" value="7"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(7) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Dental and Vision Services </label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[16]" value="8"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(8) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Drug and Alchohol Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[17]" value="10"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(10) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Family and Maternity Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[29]" value="30"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(30) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Womxn's Health Services</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[18]" value="15"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(15) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >General Health Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[19]" value="16"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(16) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    > HIV/AIDS Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[20]" value="22"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(22) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Mental Health Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[31]" value="32"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(32) >= 0) { %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Problem Gambling Resources</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[32]" value="31"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(31) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Pets and Service Animals</label>
            </section>
            <section id="financial">
                <h4>Financial, Legal, and Employment</h4>
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[21]" value="2"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(2) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Identification Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[22]" value="9"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(9) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Employment and Training Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[23]" value="11"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(11) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Financial Assistance</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[24]" value="19"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(19) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Legal Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[25]" value="21"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(21) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Mail Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[26]" value="26"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(26) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Storage Services</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[27]" value="23"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(23) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Re-entry Assistance</label> 
                <label><input type="checkbox" name="category[28]" value="28"
                    <% if (organization.array_agg.indexOf(28) >= 0){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                    >Transportation Services</label> 
            </section>
        </div>
        </div>
        <p class="script hidden">Do you need an ID or any specific documents to access services? <br><span class="emphasis">Make a note at the end of the description field above if any specifics about required documents are given.</span></p>
        <div id="final-checks">
            <h3>Additional Information</h3>
            <fieldset>
                <label>
                <input type="checkbox" value="t" name="id_req"
                    <% if (organization.id_req){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                > ID or specific documents are required to access services</label>
            </fieldset>
            <p class="script hidden">Would your agency be interested in supporting the publication of the Resource Guide with a Sponsorship? Your logo would be printed on the back of the guidebook in addition to other benefits.  We have a number of different options and pricing and we could have staff follow up with you directly.<br><span>If yes, please make a note of their email address below.</span></p>
            <fieldset>
                <label>
                <input type="checkbox" value="t" name="sponsorship"
                    <% if (organization.sponsorship){ %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                >This organization is interested in sponsorship</label>
                <label class="checks-email"><span>Email address for follow up regarding sponsorship:</span>
                <textarea type="text" name="sponsorship_email"><%= organization.sponsorship_email %></textarea></label>
            </fieldset>
            <p class="script hidden">Would you like to be on our list for distribution when the new guide is out in the late Fall? <br><span class="emphasis">If yes, please make a note of their email address below.</span></p>
            <fieldset>
                <label>
                <input type="checkbox" value="t" name="distribution"
                    <% if (organization.distribution) { %>
                        checked
                    <% } %>
                >This organization is interested in distribution</label>
                <label class="checks-email"><span>Email address to follow up regarding distribution:</span>
                <textarea type="text" name="distribution_email"><%= organization.distribution_email %></textarea>
            </label>
            </fieldset>
        </div>
        <textarea class="hidden" name="prior_cats"> <%= organization.array_agg %> </textarea>
        <input class="hidden" name="timestamp" id="timestamp">
        <p class="script hidden"><span class="emphasis">Even if no updates were made to this organization's information, hit the submit button below so it is noted that this record has been checked.</span></p>
        <button type="submit">Submit</button>
      </form>
</main>
